sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant Application
    participant EnableBanking
    participant Bank
    
    Client->>Application: GET /authorize
    Application->>EnableBanking: Request authorization URL
    EnableBanking-->>Application: Return access URL
    Application-->>Client: Redirect to access URL
    
    Client->>Bank: User lands on bank page
    Note over Client,Bank: User performs authorization
    Bank-->>Client: Authorization complete
    
    Bank->>Application: Redirect to /callback with code
    Note over Application: Receives code parameter
    
    Application->>EnableBanking: POST /session (with code)
    EnableBanking-->>Application: Return session with session_id
    
    Application->>EnableBanking: GET /session/{id}
    EnableBanking-->>Application: Return list of accounts
    
    Application->>EnableBanking: GET /accounts/{id}
    EnableBanking-->>Application: Return account details
    
    Application-->>Client: Display account information
